13. error severity can be set at project level. For that dbt_project.yml needs to be updated as below:

tests:
  asmit_prj: 
    +severity: warn

But for any particular column of any table/model if you want to set serverity as error, you can set it up in that individual yml file of that model 

We can also set some threshold in severity as below 

    +severity: warn
      warn_if: ">0"
      error_if: ">100"


